@jhart1685 Yes, I’m basically suggesting that, except that `ErrorCodeManifestUnknown` is not quite an `error`. Compare the recently-added https://github.com/containers/image/blob/29aec5f7bbbf6d58cf377f7d2aaf9ac32ba2bfa0/docker/docker_client.go#L923-L934. Caveats:
- It’s very likely that _doesn’t work_ reliably against the full universe of registries.
- c/image _does not_ document or promise that it will continue returning that return type; compare https://github.com/containers/image/pull/1487 which already proposes to change some parts of the returned error value.
